Coding helps us to communicate with our computer, and develop different apps that make our life easier. Whenever you write a letter on the keyboard the computer takes that letter
turn it into binary numbers and print out the process it is supposed to do.The computer takes input from the user for example when we enter our password to enter the computer it 
takes our input than if the password is correct it let us enter the computer which is the output.
Software Developers sell so many of them that they actually have to come up with new categories of infinitely reproducible nothings just to handle what happened with the last batch
